Tsarnaev's mother, Zubeidat Tsarnaeva, confirmed to the New York Times  on Wednesday that her older son knew Todashev.

In a telephone interview from 
Dagestan, Tsarnaeva said Todashev moved from Boston to Florida about two
 years ago. She said she is devastated to learn that he has been killed.

'Now another boy has left this life,' 
she told the newspaper. 'Why are they killing these children without any
 trial or investigation?'

The FBI has been 
