 regarding his ties to Tamerlan Tsarnaev, who was killed by 
police in a shootout following the deadly April 15 marathon bombings. Dzhokhar Tsarnaev, 19, has been charged in connection with the bombings 
and is being held at a prison medical center outside Boston.

